------------------------
Introductory information
------------------------

Generated in +1 ionic s2 configuration; semicore sp shells included.

Modified version of a potential generated by me personally in 1999.

--------------------
Intended environment
--------------------

Mostly for Sc in oxides where it is in the 3+ formal oxidation
state.

---------------------------------------
Summary of atomic transferability tests
---------------------------------------

There is a test for the s1d1 configuration in the distribution:

   nlm    all-elec      pseudo        diff

   300   -4.541304   -4.540781   -0.000523
   310   -2.986543   -2.985920   -0.000623
   400   -0.732001   -0.731900   -0.000101
   320   -0.751790   -0.752484    0.000694

